{"id": "1201885565562404906", "channel_id": "1201885565562404906", "type": 0, "author_id": "830435120590487562", "author_name": "0620n", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問時間原點不能回溯限定池角色和命輪嗎？\n像是紅夫人或者圖魯\n命途回溯之芯能否放到下個月或者幾個月後選當期限定命輪？\n靈魂回溯之心能否放到下個月或者幾個月後選當期限定角色？", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T13:44:08.784000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-30T13:47:11.480000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201885565562404906", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」時間原點", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1201889371750666273", "channel_id": "1201885565562404906", "type": 0, "author_id": "726448753996857384", "author_name": "thesongoftheeternity", "author_bot": false, "content": "時間原點的出現本質上是達芙戴爾事件的補償 所以 應該跟圖魯與夫人無關  另外兩點根據 貓 的回答{與時間推進} 應該可以留", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T13:59:16.250000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-30T13:59:49.552000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201885565562404906", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」時間原點", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1201999136136896534", "channel_id": "1201885565562404906", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "這些好像都是當初討論已經有結論的問題\n\n首先，時間原點只能用於回溯常駐角色、命輪，\n索蕾爾跟圖魯的角色、命輪按理不在對象內\n\n命途、靈魂回溯之薪都可以放\n有使用時間限定的只有時間原點\n以及達芙、藏品限時開啟的回溯功能", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T21:15:26.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201885565562404906", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」時間原點", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
