{"id": "1201804009938362388", "channel_id": "1201804009938362388", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181998298282868826", "author_name": "art1_2_3", "author_bot": false, "content": "描述是“图鲁消耗算力时”，理论上非0费灵智觉醒卡打出去也确实消耗算力（因为能获得银钥能量，而这是银钥充能机制），但是实际上觉醒卡打出去并不会触发相应觉醒效果，这是不是什么隐藏设定", "timestamp": "2024-01-30T08:20:04.408000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1201804009938362388", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于图鲁的灵智觉醒", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497"]}
